1851851851851" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2444" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(119, 140, 163);border-radius: 20px;height: auto;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7Qt6decVvmECSic5R7W6xsvlg3840UevbuiaUMCKwfDB6slbDQEB8I0NAyKxrJq2UhAic9uicmlxenvsA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="text-align: center;margin: 8px 8px 16px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">把选择部分翻译成日语</span></p><h4 style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;">2.&nbsp;马斯克追踪者</span></strong></span></h4><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;">专注于马斯克动态，及时通知其最新情况，信息来源可靠，更新迅速。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;">网址：</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;">https://chatglm.cn/main/gdetail/65bc403349828c64d52e5e1e</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;">比如问它昨天的新闻马斯克起诉 Open AI，第一次回答的一般。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="367" data-backw="558" data-height="1398" data-imgfileid="100073098" data-ratio="0.6574074074074074" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="2128" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(119, 140, 163);border-radius: 20px;height: auto;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7Qt6decVvmECSic5R7W6xsvlcDSNljIHVicXiaXeU325ZicxZMtJ5uXw7KHD1E7JJtFYgOs3iaK40AJmRA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="text-align: center;margin: 8px 8px 16px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">第一次提问</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;">第二次又继续缩小范围让他回答，它可以立马总结梳理清楚，我都不用费老劲刷新闻了！可见对于新闻追踪是一把好手。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;">（PS：提问的时候尽可能把范围缩小，答案会更精确！）</span></p><p style="margin: 16px 8px 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="287" data-backw="558" data-height="778" data-imgfileid="100073097" data-ratio="0.5138888888888888" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="1514" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(119, 140, 163);border-radius: 20px;height: auto;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7Qt6decVvmECSic5R7W6xsvlBYANg3TdfWMtY4UGuoWnWuHXRibAwMSuW3uVNIlqMa96TLANIuJX4Yg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="text-align: center;margin: 8px 8px 16px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">第二次提问</span></p><h4 style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;">3. 互联网黑话 P9 专家</span></strong></span></h4><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;">发力快速响应，赋能行业引爆点。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><