58" data-height="530" data-imgfileid="100073127" data-ratio="0.2518518518518518" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="2108" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(119, 140, 163);border-radius: 20px;height: auto;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7Qt6decVvmECSic5R7W6xsvlWKfKhwozJFTsq9rfVcGWh59uZWoJeCjMgxcQ7ibKrRRBcy6OoByds9A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;">当然，怎么制作一个智能体上面的介绍还属于小打小闹，我们也正要举办一场关于AI 智能体的 Hackathon，详情请看下面的海报：</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin: 16px 8px 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="4189" data-backw="558" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100073130" data-ratio="7.507407407407407" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(119, 140, 163);border-radius: 20px;height: auto;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5gR6KWHNb7Qt6decVvmECSic5R7W6xsvlKAcVuicKMWWo0Uib9kTCy3qURZYH2eGLZ3jDthYbDDja7nSU94o6rfvQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;">如果感兴趣的，想报名的！或者是想赞助的！都可以扫描下面的二维码联系我。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="172" data-backw="558" data-height="180" data-imgfileid="100073128" data-ratio="0.3076923076923077" data-type="png" data-w="585" data-width="585" style="color: rgb(138, 143, 141);font-size: 14px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(119, 140, 163);border-radius: 20px;height: auto;visibility: visible !important;w