。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="750" data-backw="558" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100071144" data-ratio="1.34375" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="800" style="border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(144, 157, 172);border-radius: 20px;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/5gR6KWHNb7SnfOgaACiby03lVH6zCWxraibWje0HzYwKBMk8WUde4gtYt1vDBB4lv2DcmoA8gD4IXXhBcib9SW8TQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 76, 0);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(48, 48, 48);">第四，编写代码</span></strong></span></p><p style="min-height: 24px;margin: 16px 8px 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(48, 48, 48);">能辅助理解和编写代码，有什么代码相关的问题统统砸过来！</span><em style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></em></p><p style="min-height: 24px;margin: 16px 8px 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="font-size: 16px;">场景：自动化编写脚本</span></em></span></p><p style="text-align: center;min-height: 24px;margin: 16px 8px 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="458" data-backw="558" data-imgfileid="100071149" data-ratio="0.8216666666666667" data-type="gif" data-w="600" style="font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsof